{"tid":854702,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"為左男朋友學睇波","createTime":"2018-10-09T14:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T17:41:06.000Z","uid":145758,"like":58,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4e52ce12c85929f5c3d36ee5889efbcbb3f8e05b","tid":854702,"uid":145758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"有時打開google見到有波睇<br />\n我知佢一定都有睇緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲記得佢教我係reddit搵stream一齊睇<br />\n<br />\n為左可以陪佢睇波同融入佢世界<br />\n成日叫佢教我足球既野<br />\n自己係連登睇住啲足球post學下術語<br />\n睇下人地講咩 等我都可以明佢笑緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特登去搵邊個邊個球員個名記住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我記得佢買左件波衫比我<br />\n著住去大球場一齊睇利物浦<br />\n雖然我到依加都係學到半桶水咁識dd咁<br />\n<br />\n諗起個陣我地夜晚各自係hall<br />\n雖然隔住好遠 但都一齊捱夜睇住利入4強同決賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我記得佢好開心 仲話見到我好似半個利迷咁<br />\n個下覺得我努力學足球既野係無白費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為左佢我好努力學好多野 <br />\n只係想同佢有話題可以傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有爲佢學打機 雖然好幼稚<br />\n你仲記唔記得我地係minecraft起屋<br />\n記唔記你教我打lol第一次用ashe<br />\n個陣好單純好開心<br />\n<br />\n可惜最後都係要分開<br />\n算啦 都認清左要放低了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cdf0ebf35b4ab5b11b9e71a5e00ef9700b6a1b","tid":854702,"uid":85557,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"睇av啦重睇波"},{"pid":"c2e31f7a02690709e2b9c9840ceab284d720925d","tid":854702,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"雖然隔住好遠 但都一齊捱夜睇住利入4強同決賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1fabc2311f996712ffc6e3c1ca356e1e55d645","tid":854702,"uid":74262,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c37348d40eb5db0de17d7cf8e1bf